OL,6,FThe government is under increasing
OL,7,Fpressure to apologise for the state's
OL,8,Frole in Britain's 'horrendous' forced
OL,9,Fadoption scandal, ITV News Social
OL,10,FAffairs Correspondent Sarah Corker
OL,11,Freports
OL,13,FChrissie Sharp is only now finding out
OL,14,Fthe full truth about her birth and the
OL,15,Fextent of the "horrendous" suffering
OL,16,Fher mother faced having a baby as an
OL,17,Funmarried woman in post-war Britain.
OL,19,F"My mum remembers she was scrubbing
OL,20,Fthe floors when she went into labour,"
OL,21,FChrissie told ITV News.
