OL,6,FChrissie said her adoption had already
OL,7,Fbeen arranged for after her birth, but
OL,8,Fher mother managed to keep her on the
OL,9,Fcondition she worked for the home
OL,10,Fdelivering babies - despite having no
OL,11,Fmedical training.
OL,13,F"Yes, she was able to keep me, which
OL,14,Fwas a miracle in itself, but the
OL,15,Fconditions of her staying there and
OL,16,Fwhat she had to do was horrendous,"
OL,17,Fshe said.
