OL,6,F"Effectively I was a prisoner, I was
OL,7,Falone and I was forced to pray every
OL,8,Fsingle day and do laundry," she told
OL,9,FITV News.
OL,11,FNow an author, Karen has written about
OL,12,Fher experience and other victims and
OL,13,Fsurvivors of the scandal.
OL,15,FShe kept her son, but at a cost. She
OL,16,Fwas disowned by her family, shamed and
OL,17,Fshunned by society, and lived in
OL,18,Fpoverty with her baby.
