OL,6,F"I was homeless at 16, I applied for a
OL,7,Fcouncil house, and after many months I
OL,8,Fwas given a 'hard to let' property, a
OL,9,Fhouse no-one else on the waiting list
OL,10,Fwanted," Karen recalled.
OL,12,F"The walls ran with damp, mushrooms
OL,13,Fgrew along the edges of the rooms. It
OL,14,Fwas so cold that the toilet froze
OL,15,Fsolid. I still have very vivid and
OL,16,Freoccurring nightmares about it.
OL,18,F"The neighbours I lived amongst had a
OL,19,Fpetition to get us removed, because I
OL,20,Fwas a single parent with a toddler,"
OL,21,Fshe added.
