OL,7,Fcampaigning for an official apology,
OL,8,Fsaid the government needs to build a
OL,9,Frelationship with victims and survivors
OL,11,FIn 2021, an inquiry by the Joint
OL,12,FCommittee of Human Rights concluded
OL,13,Fthat the state bore ultimate
OL,14,Fresponsibility for the suffering
OL,15,Finflicted on vulnerable women and
OL,16,Ftheir children, calling on the
