OL,6,FAn apology will come too late for
OL,7,FJean, who died in 2006, but Chrissie
OL,8,Fand her family are determined to
OL,9,Fcontinue their fight for justice in
OL,10,Fher memory.
OL,12,F"She never got over the shame, and she
OL,13,Fshould have never have felt that, and
OL,14,Fshe should have never been made to
OL,15,Ffeel that," Chrissie said.
